Security Incident Report: Web Application Breach Analysis
1. Introduction

We recently performed a forensic deep-dive into our web application logs following a detected security breach. The goal was simple: figure out how they got in, what they touched, and how we make sure it never happens again. This report breaks down the digital breadcrumbs left by the attackers and provides a roadmap for hardening our defenses.
